<MudTabs Elevation="0" Rounded="true" ApplyEffectsToContainer="true">
    <MudTabPanel Style="background-color:transparent;" Text="Price Movement">
        <time class="block mb-2 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">
            The aim of the game is to predict whether the price of the crypto currency will rise or fall after the selected fixed duration.
        </time>

        <br />

        <ol class="relative">
            <li class="mb-10 ml-8">
                <span class="flex absolute -left-1 justify-center items-center w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 rounded-full ring-8 ring-white dark:ring-gray-900 dark:bg-blue-900">
                    1
                </span>
                <h3 class="flex items-center mb-1 mr-2 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-250 dark:text-white">Market</h3>
                <time class="block mb-2 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">Select from the predefined markets in the lobby.</time>
            </li>
            <li class="mb-10 ml-8">
                <span class="flex absolute -left-1 justify-center items-center w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 rounded-full ring-8 ring-white dark:ring-gray-900 dark:bg-blue-900">
                    2
                </span>
                <h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-250 dark:text-white">Direction</h3>
                <time class="block mb-2 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">
                    Select your desired direction based on your market prediction.
                    Will the price of the market go up or down, from the point you
                    place your bet?
                </time>
            </li>
            <li class="mb-10 ml-8">
                <span class="flex absolute -left-1 justify-center items-center w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 rounded-full ring-8 ring-white dark:ring-gray-900 dark:bg-blue-900">
                    3
                </span>
                <h3 class="mb-1 text-lg font-semibold text-gray-250 dark:text-white">Duration</h3>
                <time class="block mb-2 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">
                    Set the duration of the bet. Your bet will be placed at the current
                    price of the market. Once the duration is expired, the current price
                    of the market will be used to result.
                </time>
            </li>
            <li class="ml-8">
                <span class="flex absolute -left-1 justify-center items-center w-6 h-6 bg-blue-600 rounded-full ring-8 ring-white dark:ring-gray-900 dark:bg-blue-900">
                    4
                </span>
