                <time class="block mb-2 text-sm font-normal leading-none text-gray-400 dark:text-gray-500">
                    Enter your stake amount to receive a payout quote instantly, before
                    submitting the bet. The payout is always calculated in real time while the player is interacting with the controls to
                    place a bet.
                </time>
            </li>
        </ol>
    </MudTabPanel>

